<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title></title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width-device-width, initial-scale=2, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script>
  // compile the template
  var template = Handlebars.compile("Handlebars <b>{{doesWhat}}</b>");
  // execute the compiled template and print the output to the console
  console.log(template({ doesWhat: "rocks!" }));
    </script>
    <style>

        .gradient {
            height: 10px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #F4862c, #EC1450, #8D227E, #6E2A8F);
        }

        .main_content {
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding-left: 30px;
        }


        .bt_SendLink {
            border-radius: 20px;
            color: white;
            height: 35px;
            font-size: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 3px;
            padding-top: 2px;
            width: 100px;
            border: none;
            background: linear-gradient(#26E426, #0B420B);
        }

        .navbar {
            padding: 0%;
        }
        tr{
            border:2px solid red;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body style="border:1px solid black;padding:10px;width:100%" class="container">

    <header class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-light navbar-lg">
        <img class="logo" src="http://www.starmarksv.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Starmark_Logo_252X70.png">

    </header>
    <div class="gradient"></div>

    <div class="main_content">
        <p>Hello, %name%</p>
        <p>
            Congratulations on being selected for Starmark!<br /><br />
            We take immense pleasure in welcoming you to become part of Starmark family. You are requested to report us on %date% at %time%.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Venue:</strong></p>
        <p>
            <strong>
                Starmark Software Pvt Ltd,<br />
                16/1, Wings Building, 3rd floor,<br />
                Cambridge Road, Jogupalya,<br />
                Halasuru,<br />
                Bangalore – 560008
            </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            You might know that Onboarding does not start from day one but way earlier. Have a look at what you are suppose to do,

            <ul>
                <li>Fill up the information</li>
                <li>Upload all the requested documents</li>
                <li>Sign the Agreements from Starmark</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>If you have any queries regarding the same then please contact <a href="#"> Keerthi.kiran@starmarksv.com</a> <br /></p>
        <p><strong>Happy Onboarding!</strong></p>
        <div class="table1" id="salaryBreakup" style="margin:auto;">
            <table style="margin:auto; width: 100%; height: 50%; border:1px solid black;" class="table table-bordered table-sm">
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th colspan="2" style="text-align: center;">
                        Salary Breakup
                    </th>
                </tr>
                <tr style="color: chocolate; border:1px solid black;"">
                    <th>Components</th>
                    <th>Rs. (Per month)</th>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th>Basic Salary</th>
                    <td id="basicSal">%basicSalary%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th colspan="3">Allowances</th>
                <tr>
                    <th class="second-level-padding">House Rent Allowance</th>
                    <td id="houseRentAllow">%houseRentAllowances%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Travel Allowance</th>
                    <td id="travelAllow">%travelAllowances%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr id="NArow">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Night Shift Allowance</th>
                    <td id="nightShiftAllow">%nightShiftAllowances%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Special Allowance</th>
                    <td id="specialAllow">%specialAllowances%</td>
                </tr>
                </tr>
                <tr style="color: chocolate;border:1px solid black;" >
                    <th>Monthly Gross Salary (A)</th>
                    <td id="monthlyGrossSal">%monthlyGross%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th colspan="3">Other Benefits</th>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding" style="padding-left: 50px;">Company's PF Contribution</th>
                    <td id="compPF">%companyPF%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr id="ESIrow" style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Company's ESI Contribution</th>
                    <td id="compESI">%ESI%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr id="MIrow" style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Monthly Performance Incentive</th>
                    <td id="monthlyIncentive">%monthlyIncentive%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Premium towards Medical and Accident Group Insurance</th>
                    <td id="medicalInsur">%medicalInsurance%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border:1px solid black;">
                    <th class="second-level-padding">Gratuity</th>
                    <td id="gratuity">%gratuity%</td>
                </tr>
                </tr>
                <tr style="color: chocolate;border:1px solid black;">
                    <th>Sub Total (B)</th>
                    <td id="subtotal">%subtotal%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="color: chocolate;border:1px solid black;">
                    <th>Monthly Cost to the Company CTC (A+B)</th>
                    <td id="monthlyCTC">%monthlyCTC%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="color: chocolate;border:1px solid black;">
                    <th>Annual Cost to the Company CTC </th>
                    <td id="annualCTC">%annualCTC%</td>
                    <input type="hidden" name="ctc" value="" id="ctc" />
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div style=" width:10%;background-color: #4CAF50;padding: 5px;color: white" ">
            <strong><a style="padding:10px;text-decoration:none;color:white;" href="https://hrportalqc.vitalaxis.com//ProspectiveEmployee/Token?token=%token%">Lets Begin</a></strong>
        </div>
        <p>
            <br />
            Regards<br />
            HR Team<br />
            Starmark Software
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>